:::::Yes, WaPo is generally considered a strong reliable source. Politico is a mainstream media RS and is not a blog. Huffington Post has to be closely looked at. Generally it is considered reliable but it has quite a number of invited blog pages, columnists and op-ed writers who are reliable for their own opinions only.  [[User:Capitalismojo|Capitalismojo]] ([[User talk:Capitalismojo|talk]]) 19:42, 11 May 2014 (UTC)

